WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:04.960 --> 00:00:07.460
"-Hi everybody!
-Hello!"

00:00:07.740 --> 00:00:12.000
Peek-a-boo!

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:14.020
It's Asahi-chan!

00:00:14.200 --> 00:00:21.480
Today we're going to play with Mell-chan and Nene-chan's Waku-waku Food Court!

00:00:21.740 --> 00:00:27.680
Mell-chan and Nene-chan can go out to eat in this playset.

00:00:27.780 --> 00:00:31.440
I wonder what they'll order…Let's open it up and see!

00:00:33.053 --> 00:00:35.053
It's huge!

00:00:35.240 --> 00:00:39.780
Inside there was the food court, food…

00:00:39.780 --> 00:00:41.693
…and a table and chairs.

00:00:41.693 --> 00:00:42.973
Wow!

00:00:43.020 --> 00:00:45.600
Whoa, it spins!

00:00:45.680 --> 00:00:49.380
The tray goes here, and here's some water.

00:00:49.380 --> 00:00:51.295
Welcome!

00:00:51.300 --> 00:00:57.800
Now it is 50% off on takoyaki and egg udon noodles!

00:00:58.420 --> 00:01:00.820
"Hey, Asahi, what do you want to order?"

00:01:05.660 --> 00:01:07.140
"Egg udon? Sure!"

00:01:07.620 --> 00:01:10.340
"One egg udon, please!

00:01:10.500 --> 00:01:14.040
Once you order, step on this flower button!

00:01:16.620 --> 00:01:19.600
"Here's your egg udon!"

00:01:19.600 --> 00:01:20.969
"Yay!"

00:01:21.680 --> 00:01:24.820
It's best to carry it on this tray!

00:01:24.980 --> 00:01:27.360
I'll show you how the order system works.

00:01:27.460 --> 00:01:31.700
When you press the heart lever, a box comes in here.

00:01:32.060 --> 00:01:35.500
You put the order in it like this…

00:01:38.080 --> 00:01:39.440
…and it goes like this!

00:01:39.440 --> 00:01:41.740
"One Lovely Donut, please!"

00:01:41.740 --> 00:01:43.056
"Sure, here you go!"

00:01:44.560 --> 00:01:45.820
"Yay!"

00:01:45.940 --> 00:01:48.100
"One takoyaki set, please!"

00:01:50.080 --> 00:01:52.280
"Here you go!"

00:01:52.280 --> 00:01:59.060
"Put it on the tray… We sure ordered a lot!"

00:01:59.493 --> 00:02:01.493
"One Bear Burger, please!"

00:02:01.500 --> 00:02:03.720
"Sure, one moment please!"

00:02:03.720 --> 00:02:08.880
"Here you go! … You guys ordered too much!"

00:02:08.880 --> 00:02:14.320
"Alright, let me ring you up… Your total is 450 yen."

00:02:15.260 --> 00:02:17.260
"Here you go!"

00:02:19.720 --> 00:02:21.260
"Thank you!"

00:02:21.480 --> 00:02:28.740
Chomp chomp chomp. When you eat the food, it flips over like this!

00:02:28.980 --> 00:02:32.040
When you're done, return the dishes here!

00:02:32.040 --> 00:02:33.402
"Ok!"

00:02:35.860 --> 00:02:40.500
"Hey, big sis! I found a really good food court recently!"

00:02:40.880 --> 00:02:43.460
"Let's go check it out!"

00:02:43.460 --> 00:02:47.040
"-"I'll go get a tray."
-"Thanks!""

00:02:47.120 --> 00:02:50.880
"Thanks for visiting! What would you like?"

00:02:50.880 --> 00:02:54.140
"Let's get takoyaki."

00:02:55.800 --> 00:02:56.860
"Here it is!"

00:02:57.100 --> 00:02:59.400
"Here you go!"
"Thank you!"

00:02:59.660 --> 00:03:02.240
"Here you go, Asahi."

00:03:03.900 --> 00:03:06.060
"Nene-chan, what do you want to eat?"

00:03:06.280 --> 00:03:08.680
"A Bear Burger!"

00:03:08.680 --> 00:03:10.640
"One Bear Burger, please!"

00:03:10.640 --> 00:03:12.613
"Ok, please press the button!"

00:03:14.300 --> 00:03:15.340
"Here it is!"

00:03:15.340 --> 00:03:17.064
"One Star Curry, please!"

00:03:17.500 --> 00:03:20.360
"Sure, one second."

00:03:22.880 --> 00:03:24.440
"Yay!"

00:03:24.580 --> 00:03:26.800
"Itadakimasu!"

00:03:26.800 --> 00:03:30.700
"It's so good!"

00:03:34.540 --> 00:03:37.300
(She's a little clumsy, like Kanna-chan…)

00:03:39.458 --> 00:03:41.458
She's just like you!
Hey, that's mean!

00:03:42.439 --> 00:03:44.439
"One Lovely Donut, please!"

00:03:44.800 --> 00:03:45.960
"Sure!"

00:03:49.640 --> 00:03:52.120
"Phew, I'm full!"

00:03:52.220 --> 00:03:58.400
You can play shop with Mell-chan and Nene-chan with this fun playset.

00:03:58.400 --> 00:04:01.080
Please try it out for yourself!

00:04:01.080 --> 00:04:02.900
Byebye, come watch us again!

00:04:02.900 --> 00:04:04.524
See ya!

00:04:04.524 --> 00:04:05.842
Asahi…!

